This is a police station! Take this outside!

583
00:46:02,360 --> 00:46:03,719
This is a police station! Take this outside!

584
00:46:08,440 --> 00:46:09,360
Mui...

585
00:46:09,519 --> 00:46:11,519
I'm sorry.

586
00:46:11,800 --> 00:46:12,840
I'm sorry.

587
00:46:13,639 --> 00:46:14,719
I'm sorry.

588
